COVID-19 > Reopenings
Recent United States and Canadian Gaming Property Reopenings

1,351 gaming properties have reopened including 1,286 in the United States and 65 in Canada. 26 of the reopened properties only reopened for live racing without spectators.

The table below lists all 1,351 reopened gaming properties. You can sort the table by any column and you can click a property name to view additional property details.
